-pockethrms </a></h3><h4>02 November 2023 10:00:51 AM</h4></div></div><p>Obtaining a relieving letter is important for employees who have left a company as it serves as proof of employment and can be necessary for future job opportunities. If you haven&#8217;t received a relieving letter, you can take the following steps to obtain one: Contact HR: Reach out to your forme</p></div></div><div class="feed-footer"><div><img class="me-2" src="./assets/img/icon/view.png" /><span class="me-2">65 Views</span><img class="me-2" src="./assets/img/icon/replies.png" /><span class="me-2">4 Replies</span><img class="me-2" src="./assets/img/icon/ratting.png" /><span class="me-2">1 Appreciations</span></div><div><img src="./assets/img/icon/bookmark.png" /></div></div></div><div class='feed feed-new' id='postid_2501474' data-order='1698839914'><div class='feedpad'><h2><a href='/showthread.php?t=643583'>Difference In Agreements Between Companies, And Between A Company And A Person In The Case Of Consultants?</a></h2><input type='hidden' name='lastimp' value='1698839914'><div class='badge-wrap'><lable class='badge-lbl'><a href='https://www.citehr.com/tags.php?tag=City-India-Kochi'>City-India-Kochi</a></lable><lable class='badge-lbl'><a href='https://www.citehr.com/tags.php?tag=+clause+in+agreement'> Clause In Agreement</a></lable><lable class='badge-lbl'><a href='https://www.citehr.com/tags.php?tag=+Country-India'> Country-India</a></lable></div><div class="profile"><div class="rounded-letter me-3 user-icon">PC</div><h3><a href="/member.php?u=4615470" class="userlink">Priyaslakshmi1905@gmail.com </a><span><a href="/profile.php?do=addlist&userlist=friend&u=4615470">Follow</a></span></h3><p>Greetings all, Is there any difference between the agreements written between companies and between company and person in the case of consultants? Specially the clause Assignment The Services to be performed by the consultant hereunder are personal in nature, and Company has engaged Consultant as a re