d. Rejection happens only in case mismatch in given name, surname etc. Also you should ensure your name with initial should look alike both in PF UAN and Bank Account.</p></div><div class='replay-wrap' id='reply_2500427'><div class='replay-profile'><img height="50px" width="50px" class="rounded-circle object-fit-cover me-3 user-icon" src="/customprofilepics/profilepic1264621_1.gif" alt="" id="contribimg"><div><h3><a href='/member.php?u=1264621' class='userlink'>Bijay_majumdar </a></h3><h4>04 October 2023 16:13:43 PM</h4></div></div><p>Name in your account, Your aadhar and UAN should be same.It is also important that you account should be adhar linked. Salutation is not the problem.Also the cheque or passbook which you submit for account verification must have same name.</p></div></div><div class="feed-footer"><div><img class="me-2" src="./assets/img/icon/view.png" /><span class="me-2">10 Views</span><img class="me-2" src="./assets/img/icon/replies.png" /><span class="me-2">2 Replies</span><img class="me-2" src="./assets/img/icon/ratting.png" /><span class="me-2">0 Appreciations</span></div><div><img src="./assets/img/icon/bookmark.png" /></div></div></div><div class='feed feed-new' id='postid_2500425' data-order='1696428784'><div class='feedpad'><h2><a href='/showthread.php?t=643203'>Looking For Shops And Establishment Minimum Wages Tamilnadu 2022-23</a></h2><input type='hidden' name='lastimp' value='1696428784'><div class='badge-wrap'><lable class='badge-lbl'><a href='https://www.citehr.com/tags.php?tag=City-India-Mumbai'>City-India-Mumbai</a></lable><lable class='badge-lbl'><a href='https://www.citehr.com/tags.php?tag=+Country-India'> Country-India</a></lable><lable class='badge-lbl'><a href='https://www.citehr.com/tags.php?tag=+factories+act'> Factories Act</a></lable><lable class='badge-lbl'><a href='https://www.citehr.com/tags.php?tag=+minimum+wages'> Minimum Wages</a></lable><lable class='badge-lbl'><a href='https://www.citehr.com/tags.php?tag=+minimum+wages+t